<!--App.vue-->
<template>
  <TestComp @fromChild="update">{{num}}</TestComp>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'App',
  data() {
    return {
      num: 0
    }
  },
  methods: {
    update(a) {
      this.num = a;
    }
  },
}
</script>

<style>
body {
    padding-top: 90px;
}
</style>
